
when answering please be as specific as possible the more details the better….
 
·   Please provide a suggestion you made during your current project. Why did you make the suggestion? What did they do with your suggestion?
·   For your last 2 projects provide the following
o   What was the project about
o   What did you contribute
o   Did you have any issues/problems? If so please explain how you resolved them
o   What was the end result
 
Monsanto looks for resumes that explains what YOU have done, not just list a bunch of bullet points. They want to know what and WHY you use the tool/language…
